br />\n<ins>引言</ins><br />\n<br />\n廿一世紀最偉大的發明 - 神念系統。 <br />\n<br />\n所謂「神」，即是用植入於身體內的超級電腦晶片去尋找最佳的神經脈衝傳遞方式，從而最有效率地活動。由此，人類的協調力、速度、力量等都有突破性的進步。 <br />\n<br />\n所謂「念」，即利用腦電波控制機械活動。 <br />\n<br />\n能夠將兩者充份發揮，並且相輔相乘，就能達到人機合一的境界 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>FACEBOOK PAGE</ins> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80-1462408737419954/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25B8%2580-1462408737419954%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c81cead4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80-1462408737419954/</a><br />\n包含最新情報、第一至第三十二話，喜歡既巴絲就請比個LIKE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dw <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>章節</ins><br />\n第一話至第十一話 ~ 捉迷藏篇<br />\n第十二話至第二十二話 ~ 飛行棋篇<br />\n第二十三話至第？話 ~ 最新篇"},{"pid":"04f6a4755cb3c1b822b93f56e4cd8455bfdd1bf1","tid":105821,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:18:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">第三十三話 - MIRROR ON THE WALL III</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i77.photobucket.com/albums/j64/Tyfong91/S33TP1_zpsxac1cn7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi77.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fj64%2FTyfong91%2FS33TP1_zpsxac1cn7g.png&h=fad46858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i77.photobucket.com/albums/j64/Tyfong91/S33TP2_zps9h4trvwj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi77.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fj64%2FTyfong91%2FS33TP2_zps9h4trvwj.png&h=4a84474f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i77.photobucket.com/albums/j64/Tyfong91/S33TP3_zpscpphmxo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi77.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fj64%2FTyfong91%2FS33TP3_zpscpphmxo8.png&h=c464885b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i77.photobucket.com/albums/j64/Tyfong91